headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Imbs Holdings, Inc.
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of St. Louis, Missouri-based Imbs Holdings, Inc. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
